{"tid":1852251,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"就算醫護唔罷工，都應該要爭取同黑警相同或更高待遇","createTime":"2020-01-30T10:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T11:27:45.000Z","uid":14678,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b84067320f431deab96ef492dfd3c9743a3fb7cc","tid":1852251,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:57:34.000Z","msg":"7個月過去，黑警無死過一個<br />\n但係日日企係到，甚或坐喺到就賺到幾倍所謂OT 津貼。一個月閒閒地都10萬8萬，低付出高回報，無風險，犯法又唔洗付責。<br />\n<br />\n憑咩拎咁多人工？<br />\n<br />\n相反，我地睇下醫護<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 高風險</span></span><br />\n中咗支那肺炎隨時命都無，醫到身體都重傷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 高Workload</span></span><br />\nOn call 36小時就真係隨時做足36小時<br />\n休息？隨時無<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 會被問責</span></span><br />\n早幾日屯門醫院個Patient無入到負壓房<br />\n比人屌到要出嚟Say Sorry<br />\n陣間做錯少少又話Record 留7年<br />\n<br />\n呢份工高風險低回報仲隨時命都無，點解仲要同你博？<br />\n<br />\n所以，要爭取疫症時期 人工3倍起！不論是否isolation ward！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">醫護，罷工！<br />\n香港人，罷工！<br />\n齊上齊落<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ce13a648caea97e3e2988cc5ec51a7a69a6e538e","tid":1852251,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:58:22.000Z","msg":"反送中運動續集：口罩革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n獨立最佳時機，香港人，把握機會，反佢老母！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47sjZ7p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47sjZ7p.jpg&h=345723b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港獨立，港中區隔！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNOWhT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNOWhT4.jpg&h=e6afb774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4021e7dcdd5651a17ca51f84dac73cb5b2dfd00","tid":1852251,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:58:54.000Z","msg":"自推20連"},{"pid":"2db106be611703920f617ba3d56b1e378081675a","tid":1852251,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:59:22.000Z","msg":"自推20連"},{"pid":"5cd70a938408291d2a994b4d2cabfce5bbdf0303","tid":1852251,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:00:08.000Z","msg":"自推20連"},{"pid":"f1e4fa4821f98a4fec72690160110d3d0672277a","tid":1852251,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:00:31.000Z","msg":"自推20連"},{"pid":"012a9f270eca7af533a258f3e7cdc4862577990e","tid":1852251,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"自推20連"},{"pid":"ffb488b12f6f43983615b2fc3a89319f7eabbaca","tid":1852251,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:01:08.000Z","msg":"自推20連"},{"pid":"97b2c594a6f7728567713fa5813ca109f4818d16","tid":1852251,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:01:36.000Z","msg":"自推20連"},{"pid":"02f77a7394058dc7720ab6288f5a48ea924e7537","tid":1852251,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:01:43.000